#######
# 5: Mouse and Key bindings
#
# Contexts:
#     R = Root Window                 rrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrr
#     W = Application Window          rIrrrr<---------^rrrrr
#     F = Frame Corners               rrrrrr[13TTTT642]rrrrr
#     S = Frame Sides                 rIrrrr[wwwwwwwww]rrrrr
#     T = Title Bar                   rrrrrr[wwwwwwwww]rrrrr
#     I = Icon                        rIrrrrv_________>rrrrr
#                                     rrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrr
#
#     Numbers are buttons: [1 3 5 7 9  TTTTT  0 8 6 4 2]
#
# Modifiers: (A)ny, (C)ontrol, (S)hift, (M)eta, (N)othing
#
# Format: Key <X>  <Context> <Modifier> <Action>
#         Mouse <X> <Context> <Modifier> <Action>
####################

# Alt-F1 or Menu to load the root menu and Alt-Tab for a WindowList.
# Ctrl-F1/F2/F3/F4 will switch between the Virtual Desktops.
#
# Silent supresses any errors (such as keyboards with no Menu key).
Silent Key F1 A M Menu MenuFvwmRoot
Silent Key Menu A A Menu MenuFvwmRoot
Silent Key Tab A M WindowList Root c c NoDeskSort, SelectOnRelease Meta_L
Silent Key F1 A C GotoDesk 0 0
Silent Key F2 A C GotoDesk 0 1
Silent Key F3 A C GotoDesk 0 2
Silent Key F4 A C GotoDesk 0 3
Silent Key Return A 4 Exec exec $[infostore.terminal]
Silent Key XF86AudioRaiseVolume A N Exec amixer sset Master unmute && amixer sset Master 5%+
Silent Key XF86AudioLowerVolume A N Exec amixer sset Master unmute && amixer sset Master 5%-
Silent Key XF86AudioMute A N Exec exec amixer sset Master mute
Silent Key KP_Add A 4 Exec amixer sset Master unmute && amixer sset Master 5%+
Silent Key KP_Subtract A 4 Exec amixer sset Master unmute && amixer sset Master 5%-
Silent Key KP_Insert A 4 Exec exec amixer sset Master mute
Silent Key XF86MonBrightnessDown A N Exec exec xbacklight -dec 10
Silent Key XF86MonBrightnessUp A N Exec exec xbacklight -inc 10
Silent Key XF86AudioPlay A N Exec exec strawberry --play-pause
Silent Key XF86AudioPrev A N Exec exec strawberry --restart-or-previous
Silent Key XF86AudioNext A N Exec exec strawberry --next
Silent Key KP_End A 4 Exec exec strawberry --play-pause
Silent Key KP_Divide A 4 Exec exec strawberry --restart-or-previous
Silent Key KP_Multiply A 4 Exec exec strawberry --next

# XXX
# Key space A 4 Menu MenuFvwmRoot
# Key Menu A 4 Menu MenuFvwmRoot
# Key Tab A 4 WindowList Root c c NoDeskSort, SelectOnRelease Super_L, CurrentAtEnd, IconifiedAtEnd
# # Key Tab A S4 WindowList Root c c NoDeskSort, SelectOnRelease Super_L, CurrentAtEnd, IconifiedAtEnd, ReverseOrder
# Key 1 A 4 GotoDesk 0 0
# Key 2 A 4 GotoDesk 0 1
# Key 3 A 4 GotoDesk 0 2
# Key 4 A 4 GotoDesk 0 3
# Key 1 A S4 MovetoDesk 0 0
# Key 2 A S4 MovetoDesk 0 1
# Key 3 A S4 MovetoDesk 0 2
# Key 4 A S4 MovetoDesk 0 3
# Key Prior A 4 GotoPage 0p -1p
# Key Next A 4 GotoPage 0p +1p
# Key Prior A S4 MovetoPage 0p -1p
# Key Next A S4 MovetoPage 0p +1p
# Key m A 4 ResizeMove frame 78wa 89wa 85p 30p
# Key f A 4 Maximize Fullscreen
# Key Left A S4 ResizeMoveMaximize frame 50wa 100wa 0 0
# Key Right A S4 ResizeMoveMaximize frame 50wa 100wa -0 0
# Key Left A 4 ResizeMove frame 50wa 50wa 0 keep
# Key Right A 4 ResizeMove frame 50wa 50wa -0 keep
# Key Up A 4  ResizeMove frame 50wa 50wa keep 0
# Key Down A 4 ResizeMove frame 50wa 50wa keep -0
# # Mod4 Left :MacroCmd {ResizeTo 50% 50%} {MoveTo 00 * Left}
# # Mod4 Right :MacroCmd {ResizeTo 50% 50%} {MoveTo 00 * Right}
# # Mod4 Down :MacroCmd {ResizeTo 50% 50%} {MoveTo * 00 Bottom}
# # Mod4 Up :MacroCmd {ResizeTo 50% 50%} {MoveTo * 00 Top}
# # Mod4 Shift Left :MacroCmd {ResizeTo 50% 100%} {MoveTo 00 00 Left}
# # Mod4 6 :MacroCmd {ResizeTo 92% 92%} {MoveTo 00 00 Center}
# # Mod4 7 :MacroCmd {ResizeTo 55% 100%} {MoveTo 00 00 Left}
# # Mod4 8 :MacroCmd {ResizeTo 45% 50%} {MoveTo 00 00 TopRight}
# # Mod4 9 :MacroCmd {ResizeTo 45% 50%} {MoveTo 00 00 BottomRight}
# # Mod4 0 :Maximize
# # Mod4 Shift Right :MacroCmd {ResizeTo 50% 100%} {MoveTo 00 00 Right}
# # Mod4 Shift Up :ToggleCmd {Maximize} {Restore}
# # Mod4 Shift Down :Minimize

# XXX
# Key Pause WTSF1246 N Thumbnail

# Window Buttons: [1 3 5 7 9  TTTTT  0 8 6 4 2]
#   1 - Open the WindowOps menu.
#   2 - Close on single click, Destory on double click.
#   4 - Maximize (right/middle button will only maximize vertical/horizontal)
#   6 - Iconify (minimize)
Mouse 1 1 A Menu MenuWindowOps Delete
Mouse 1 2 A Close
Mouse 1 4 A Maximize 100 100
Mouse 2 4 A Maximize 0 100
Mouse 3 4 A Maximize 100 0
Mouse 1 6 A Thumbnail
# XXX
# Mouse 1 I A Iconify off

#   TitleBar: Click to Raise, Move, Double Click to Maximize
#             Mouse Wheel Up/Down to WindowShade On/Off
#   Borders: Click to raise, Move to Resize
#   Root Window: Left Click - Main Menu
#                Right Click - WindowOps Menu
#                Middle Click - Window List Menu
#   Right click TitleBar/Borders for WindowOps Menu
Mouse 1	T    A RaiseMoveX Move Maximize
Mouse 1	FS   A RaiseMove Resize
Mouse 4	T    A WindowShade True
Mouse 5	T    A WindowShade False
Mouse 1	R    A Menu MenuFvwmRoot
Mouse 2	R    A WindowList
Mouse 3	R    A Menu MenuWindowOpsLong
Mouse 1	I    A RaiseMoveX Move "Iconify off"
Mouse 3	T    A Menu MenuWindowOps
Mouse 3 I    A Menu MenuIconOps
Mouse 2 T    A Function MoveOrLower

